\\n- Maintain micro-continuity (hand positions, gaze direction, body orientation)\\n\\n────────────────────────\\nSHOT LIST\\n────────────────────────\\n{{PANEL_LIST}}\",\"description\":\"镜头二十五宫格图片生成\",\"categoryId\":\"cml4qy2t20000wbk14bz6kn5j\",\"type\":\"system\",\"systemId\":null,\"tags\":[\"shotImage\",\"二十五宫格\"],\"isActive\":false}','::1','success',NULL,'2026-03-03 08:31:24.210'),('cmmadjwdc011t10vpyr6stun4','cmkm9hsxx0000131b8g0q2llm','UPDATE_PROMPT','prompt','cml4x1txu002cp3j50f0pjpwz','{\"functionKey\":\"exterior_oriental_gc_anime\",\"title\":\"外景-场景图-东方GC动漫\",\"content\":\"Oriental high-end CG anime cinematic realism,\\nblending subtle ink-wash aesthetics inspired by traditional Chinese painting,\\nwhile maintaining structural clarity and scene continuity.\\nRealistic spatial structure and proportions,\\nwith refined Chinese classical architectural influence.\\nHigh-quality CG materials with natural wear and surface detail,\\nenhanced by delicate ink-wash brushstroke textures.\\nLighting is soft, warm, and poetic,\\nwith gentle contrast and physically motivated illumination.\\nAtmosphere is subtle and restrained,\\nwith slight ink-wash tonal effects used only to enhance depth and emotional tone.\\nThe environment should feel:\\n- cinematic\\n- grounded\\n- elegant\\n- emotionally warm\\n- structurally consistent across shots\\nAllow subtle ink-wash textures, atmospheric brush effects,\\nand soft traditional painting-inspired shading,\\nwithout distorting spatial logic or object placement.\",\"description\":\"外景-场景图-东方GC动漫\",\"categoryId\":\"cml4qy2t20000wbk14bz6kn5j\",\"type\":\"system_user\",\"systemId\":\"cml4uc3l8000jp3j5yesbz0ah\",\"tags\":[\"外景\",\"场景图\",\"东方GC动漫\"],\"isActive\":false}','::1','success',NULL,'2026-03-03 08:57:26.688'),('cmmadmhxh011z10vpxesnr7qs','cmkm9hsxx0000131b8g0q2llm','UPDATE_PROMPT','prompt','cmmabq5mo010710vppdnf3mo1','{\"functionKey\":\"twentyfive_panel_generator_image\",\"title\":\"镜头二十五宫格\",\"content\":\"You are a profession