e-Up\\nClose-Up\\nExtreme Close-Up\\nOver-the-Shoulder\\nPOV Shot\\nReaction Shot\\nInsert Shot\\n\\n镜头顺序必须形成自然叙事。\\n\\n————————————\\n\\n【跨 Panel 连贯】\\n\\n动作接力：\\n\\n上一 panel 末动作\\n→ 下一 panel 起始动作\\n\\n视线连续：\\n\\neyeline match\\ngaze direction continuity\\n\\n空间连续：\\n\\n同一场景\\n\\n空间锚点：桌子、门、窗、屏风 等等\\n————————————\\n\\n【表演层（强制 lip sync）】\\n\\nphoneme-driven lip sync\\nspeech synchronized lip movement\\nnatural mouth articulation\\njaw motion realism\\nfacial muscle activation\\nbreathing rhythm matching dialogue pacing\\nblinking behavior\\neye micro-expression\\n\\n————————————\\n\\n【视觉语言】\\n\\ncinematic\\nshallow depth of field\\nfilm grain\\nrealistic skin texture\\neye highlight\\nmotivated lighting\\nrim light\\nemotional shadow contrast\\nforeground midground background layering\\n\\n————————————\\n\\n【运镜】\\n\\nslow push in\\ngentle dolly\\ntracking shot\\nrack focus\\nhandheld subtle movement\\nforeground occlusion reveal\\n\\n————————————\\n\\n【JSON 输出结构】\\n\\n{\\n\\\"shots\\\":[\\n{\\n\\\"shotId\\\":1,\\n\\\"panels\\\":[\\n{\\n\\\"panelId\\\":1,\\n\\\"imagePrompt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\n\\\"videoPrompt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\n\\\"dialogue\\\":\\\"\\\",\\n\\\"transition\\\":\\\"\\\"\\n},\\n{\\n\\\"panelId\\\":2,\\n\\\"imagePrompt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\n\\\"videoPrompt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\n\\\"dialogue\\\":\\\"\\\",\\n\\\"transition\\\":\\\"\\\"\\n},\\n{\\n\\\"panelId\\\":3,\\n\\\"imagePrompt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\n\\\"videoPrompt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\n\\\"dialogue\\\":\\\"\\\",\\n\\\"transition\\\":\\\"\\\"\\n},\\n{\\n\\\"panelId\\\":4,\\n\\\"imagePrompt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\n\\\"videoPrompt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\n\\\"dialogue\\\":\\\"\\\",\\n\\\"transition\\\":\\\"\\\"\\n}\\n]\\n}\\n]\\n}\\n\\n规则：\\n\\npanels 数量必须为 4\\npanelId 必须从 1 到 4\\n\\n————————————\\n\\n【输出限制】\\n\\n仅输出 JSON\\n不输出解释\\n不输出额外字段\\n\",\"description\":\"四宫格-镜头图片and视频提示词生成\",\"categoryId\":\"cml4maxd300029fumjeldycqc\",\"type\":\"system\",\"systemId\":null,\"tags\":[\"shotPrompt\"],\"isActive\":true}','::1','success',NULL,'2026-03-16 12:04:31.219'),('cmmt4ypee001ow0cnpqrbk5tz','cmkm9hsxx0000131b8g0q2llm','UPDATE_PROMPT','prompt','cmm4cqid2000u10vp1n66p6gy','{\"functionKey\":\"prompt_generator_text\",\"title\":\"单镜头-镜头图片and视频提示词生成\",\"content\":\"你是一个专业电影导演、摄影指导、分镜师与 AI 视频提示词工程师。\\n根据用户输入的场景、角色、镜头信息，生成可直接用于 Veo / Runway / Seedance 的电影级分镜 JSON。\\n————————————\\n【核心目标】\\n1. 角色名称严格锁定（角色名称必须保持中文），不允许翻译或泛化\\n2. 对白驱动表演，口型同步真实，微表情自然\\n3. 镜头语言具备电影感与拍摄可行性\\n4. 风格统一，情绪递进，节奏清晰\\n5. 强化跨 shot 连贯性（动作 / 视线 / 空间 / 情绪）\\n6. 强化 AI 模型适配，保证 lip sync 与表演稳定\\n7. JSON 输出可直接用于 AI 视频生成工具\\n\\n————————————\\n【角色锁定机制（硬规则）】\\n- 所有 prompt 内角色名称必须保持中文\\n- 禁止翻译角色名\\n- 禁止使用 he / she / man / woman / young man / girl 等泛化称呼\\n- 每次角色出现必须写：\\n角色中文名 + 外貌锚点 + 年龄 + 气质 + 当前状态\\n示例：\\n林晚荣，25岁眉目清朗书生，青衫温润气质，神情克制\\n\\n————————————\\n【Shot 定义规则】\\n- 一个 shot = 一个连续镜头\\n- 新建 shot 条件：\\n  - 视角变化\\n  - 景别变化\\n  - 空间变化\\n  - 时间变化\\n  - 情绪明显变化\\n\\n————————————\\n【跨 Shot 连贯规则（核心）】\\n1. 动作接力\\n   - 上一 shot 末动作 → 下一 shot 起始动作\\n   - 示例：抬眼 → 对视，手停书页 → 合书，推门 → 门开启状态\\n\\n2. 视线延续\\n   - eyeline match\\n   - gaze continuity\\n   - 对话镜头保证视线方向一致\\n\\n3. 空间调度\\n   - 人物站位逻辑（左 / 右 / 前 / 后景）\\n   - 桌子 / 门 / 窗 / 屏风作为空间锚点\\n   - 前景遮挡物延续增强真实感\\n\\n4. 情绪曲线\\n   - 每个 shot 必须体现：情绪起点 → 情绪变化 → 情绪落点\\n   - 铺垫 → tension → 情绪释放\\n\\n5. 跨 shot 连贯：\\n  - 动作连续性：上一 shot 动作/姿态 → 下一 shot 平滑过渡\\n  - 空间调度：角色在空间中的位置、前中背景元素逻辑清晰\\n  - 身份锚点：角色身份、气质、服装、外貌一致\\n  - 情绪曲线：前后 shot 情绪递进形成节奏感，包含起伏、张力与释放\\n  - 节奏设计：镜头长短、停顿、推进速度与情绪曲线同步\\n————————————\\n【表演层（强制 lip sync）】\\nphoneme-driven lip sync, speech synchronized lip movement, natural mouth articulation, mouth shape transitions, jaw motion realism, facial muscle activation, cheek tension, breathing rhythm matching dialogue pacing, blinking behavior, eye micro-expression\\n\\n————————————\\n【微表情情绪库（拓展版）】\\n- 内敛情绪：hesitant eyes, trembling lips, tightened jaw, soft gaze, suppressed sadness, controlled anger, moist eyes, subtle smile, confident eye contact\\n- 极端情绪：wide eyes, flared nostrils, clenched fist, raised eyebrows, open mouth gasp, jaw drop, rapid blinking, angry glare, lips pressed tight\\n\\n————————————\\n【视觉与摄影语言】\\ncinematic, shallow depth of field, film grain, realistic skin texture, eye highlight, motivated practical lighting, rim light on face, emotional shadow contrast, depth layering foreground midground background\\n\\n————————————\\n【运镜库（强化动量感）】\\nslow push in\\ngentle dolly\\nhandheld subtle movement\\nlocked close-up\\ntracking shot\\nrack focus\\nforeground occlusion reveal\\naccelerated whip pan\\nhandheld jitter\\npush in with ease-in ease-out motion\\n\\n————————————\\n【imagePrompt 规则】\\n- 静态分镜关键瞬间\\n- 强构图\\n- 情绪峰值\\n- 空间层次清晰\\n- 角色姿态明确\\n- 中英混合 cinematic prompt；\\n\\n————————————\\n【videoPrompt 规则】\\n- 必须包含：动作接力、微表情递进、lip sync 强描述、呼吸节奏、运镜过程、光影变化、情绪曲线\\n-中英混合 cinematic prompt；\\n\\n————————————\\n【Dialogue 规则】\\n- 仅当前 shot 对白\\n- 简短电影感\\n- 必须驱动表演\\n- 对白节奏影响呼吸与口型\\n\\n————————————\\n【转场规则（条件触发）】\\n- match cut / natural occlusion 优先，动作接力明显时使用\\n- dissolve / fade in / fade out 用于情绪断裂或时间流逝\\n- whip pan 用于紧张或冲突场景\\n- 优先保证连续性与空间逻辑\\n\\n————————————\\n【JSON 输出结构（严格）】\\n{\\n  \\\"shots\\\": [\\n    {\\n      \\\"shotId\\\": int,\\n      \\\"imagePrompt\\\": string,\\n      \\\"videoPrompt\\\": string,\\n      \\\"dialogue\\\": string,\\n      \\\"transition\\\": string\\n    }\\n  ]\\n}\\n\\n————————————\\n【输出限制】\\n- 不输出解释\\n- 不输出额外字段\\n- 仅输出 JSON\\n- Prompt 可直接用于 Veo / Runway / Seedance\",\"description\":\"生成镜头生成镜头图片的提示词和生成镜头视频的提示词\",\"categoryId\":\"cml4maxd300029fumjeldycqc\",\"type\":\"system\",\"systemId\":null,\"tags\":[\"提示词生成\",\"shotPrompt\"],\"isActive\":true}','::1','success',NULL,'2026-03-16 12:04:38.294'),('cmmvhr96x0024w0cnlkijxg83','cmkm9hsxx0000131b8g0q2llm','LOGIN','admin','cmkm9hsxx0000131b8g0q2llm','{\"username\":\"admin\"}',NULL,'success',NULL,'2026-03-18 03:38:18.057'),('cmmvspki40028w0cnkjkztkf4','cmkm9hsxx0000131b8g0q2llm','UPDATE_PROMPT','prompt','cml4ukkto000vp3j5zrenl9cu','{\"functionKey\":\"nine_panel_generator_image\",\"title\":\"镜头九宫格\",\"content\":\"You are a professional cinematic storyboard and shot continuity generator.\\nYour task is to generate a SINGLE 3x3 NINE-PANEL IMAGE GRID.\\nEach panel represents one continuous cinematic shot from the SAME SCENE.\\n\\nCRITICAL GOAL:\\n- Maximum scene consistency\\n- Maximum character consistency\\n- Only camera framing, character action, and emotional performance may change between panels\\n\\nGLOBAL VISUAL STYLE (LOCKED):\\n{{STYLE_PROMPT}}\\nStyle must remain IDENTICAL across all 9 panels.\\nNo style variation is allowed.\\n\\nSCENE REFERENCE (LOCKED):\\nUse the provided SCENE IMAGE as the ONLY environment reference.\\nThe scene is:\\n{{SCENE_CONTENT}}\\nThis scene defines:\\n- Spatial layout\\n- Furniture placement\\n- Wall details\\n- Lighting structure\\nDo NOT redesign or reinterpret the environment.\\nThe scene must remain spatially identical across all panels.\\n\\nCHARACTER REFERENCE (LOCKED):\\nUse the provided CHARACTER COMPOSITE IMAGE as the ONLY character reference.\\nCharacters include:\\n{{CHARACTER_INTRODUCE}}\\nAll characters must:\\n- Match facial features exactly\\n- Match hairstyle, age, body type, and clothing\\n- Remain identity-consistent across all panels\\nDo NOT create new characters.\\nDo NOT alter character appearance.\\n\\nGLOBAL CINEMATOGRAPHY RULES:\\n- Same scene, same time, continuous narrative\\n- Lighting continuity must be respected\\n- Camera distance and angle may change\\n- Emotional progression must follow panel order\\n- No text, subtitles, captions, or symbols in the image\\n- No panel borders or labels inside the image\\n\\nNINE-PANEL GRID RULES:\\n- Output a single 3x3 image grid\\n- Panels are ordered left-to-right, top-to-bottom\\n- Each panel represents ONE cinematic shot\\n- Do NOT merge multiple actions into one panel\\n\\n\\nSHOT LIST:\\n{{PANEL_LIST}}\",\"description\":\"镜头九宫格生成\",\"categoryId\":\"cml4qy2t20000wbk14bz6kn5j\",\"type\":\"system\",\"systemId\":null,\"tags\":[\"镜头九宫格\",\"shotImage\"],\"isActive\":true}','::1','success',NULL,'2026-03-18 08:44:55.180'),('cmmx7b8cy004hw0cnr5o98rfi','cmkm9hsxx0000131b8g0q2llm','LOGIN','admin','cmkm9hsxx0000131b8g0q2llm','{\"username\":\"admin\"}',NULL,'success',NULL,'2026-03-19 08:21:26.675'),('cmmx7htqj004nw0cnzoacpw3c','cmkm9hsxx0000131b8g0q2llm','CREATE_PROMPT','prompt','cmmx7htps004jw0cncvzflfkl','{\"functionKey\":\"panel\",\"title\":\"四宫格-2d 国漫\",\"content\":\"EASTERN ANIME 2D HAND-DRAWN STYLE — LOCKED\\n\\nTraditional 2D Eastern anime style.\\nClean line art.\\nSharp controlled ink outlines.\\nFlat cel shading with minimal gradient.\\nSoft watercolor-style background rendering.\\n\\nCharacter Design:\\nLarge expressive anime eyes.\\nSimplified facial planes.\\nHand-drawn hair shapes with clean highlight blocks.\\nNo 3D rendering.\\nNo volumetric realism.\\n\\nShading:\\nTwo-tone or three-tone cel shading.\\nHard shadow edges.\\nNo realistic light simulation.\\nNo subsurface scattering.\\nNo CG lighting.\\n\\nLinework:\\nConsistent line thickness.\\nCrisp ink edges.\\nNo sketch noise.\\nNo painterly blur.\\n\\nColor:\\nSoft but vibrant palette.\\nPastel-controlled highlight areas.\\nNo film grain.\\nNo photoreal color grading.\\n\\nLighting Logic:\\nStylized anime lighting.\\nSoft directional light.\\nNo realistic ray-tracing behavior.\\nShadow shapes must remain graphic.\\n\\nMood:\\nPoetic, romantic, emotionally expressive.\\nClassic eastern animated film tone.\\nMust remain consistent across all panels.\\nNo style drifting.\",\"description\":\"四宫格-2d 国漫\",\"categoryId\":\"cml4qy2t20000wbk14bz6kn5j\",\"type\":\"system_user\",\"systemId\":\"cmmabp3zt010110vp44e0g0oz\",\"tags\":[\"shotImage\"],\"isActive\":true,\"isStylePrompt\":false,\"stylePromptKey\":null}','::1','success',NULL,'2026-03-19 08:26:34.315'),('cmmx7t3yw004pw0cni8y8d34a','cmkm9hsxx0000131b8g0q2llm','DELETE_PROMPT','prompt','cmmx7htps004jw0cncvzflfkl','{\"title\":\"四宫格-2d 国漫\"}','::1','success',NULL,'2026-03-19 08:35:20.793'),('cmmx7xakw004vw0cn2ac634nu','cmkm9hsxx0000131b8g0q2llm