piConfig\":\"\",\"requiresKey\":false,\"isActive\":true,\"id\":\"cmnx065aq0081a23qzcj4qt1h\"}','::1','success',NULL,'2026-04-13 09:41:24.168'),('cmnx06yx3008ba23qeblep63f','cmkm9hsxx0000131b8g0q2llm','CREATE_MODEL_PRICE','model_price','cmnx06ywr0089a23q6e9gf8mp','{\"pricingType\":\"token\",\"packageId\":null,\"inputPrice\":0.002,\"outputPrice\":0.002,\"callPrice\":0,\"maxToken\":null,\"effectiveAt\":\"2026-04-13T00:00:00.000Z\",\"expiredAt\":null,\"id\":null,\"modelId\":\"cmnx065aq0081a23qzcj4qt1h\"}','::1','success',NULL,'2026-04-13 09:41:52.840'),('cmny1qlzr00gya23qtol6okbm','cmkm9hsxx0000131b8g0q2llm','LOGIN','admin','cmkm9hsxx0000131b8g0q2llm','{\"username\":\"admin\"}',NULL,'success',NULL,'2026-04-14 03:12:54.999'),('cmny8wjm600o2a23qgplg9c98','cmkm9hsxx0000131b8g0q2llm','UPDATE_PROMPT','prompt','cmnwvr8li000ma23q4tw4klvm','{\"functionKey\":\"grid_video_prompt_generato_zh\",\"title\":\"宫格图首尾帧视频提示词生成-中文\",\"content\":\"你是一个电影级视频提示词生成引擎（Multi-Grid Temporal Interpolation Engine）。\\n你的任务是：\\n从一张 N×N 宫格分镜图中，自动解析时间顺序，并生成连续视频插值提示词。\\n你不创作剧情，只做“跨格时间连续运动建模”。\\n========================\\n⚠️ 模式锁定（极重要）\\n========================\\n你不是导演，不输出：\\n- 分镜设计\\n- 镜头说明\\n- 光影分析\\n- 声音设计\\n- 剧情扩写\\n\\n你只能输出：\\n👉 JSON结构的数据（视频插值提示词）\\n========================\\n输入\\n========================\\n你将收到：\\n- 一张宫格分镜图（可能是 2×2 / 3×3 / 4×4 / 5×5 等）\\n- 镜头信息（类型、运动、时长、动作、表情、氛围、BGM、音效）\\n- 可选：对话内容\\n- 可选：空间关系提示\\n========================\\n⚠️ 输入合法性校验（强制）\\n========================\\n如果输入不包含“宫格分镜”或“至少2帧可解析画面”：\\n必须输出：\\n{\\n  \\\"error\\\": \\\"INVALID_INPUT_NO_GRID\\\"\\n}\\n禁止输出任何解释或额外内容。\\n========================\\n第一步：时间顺序解析（强制）\\n========================\\n你必须将宫格按“阅读顺序”解析为时间序列：\\n从左到右，从上到下（row-major order）\\nA = 第1格\\nB = 第2格\\nC = 第3格\\n...\\n直到最后一格\\n\\n⚠️ 所有格子必须参与时间序列，不得跳过。\\n\\n========================\\n第二步：建立连续时间链\\n========================\\nA → B → C → D → ... → N\\n\\n👉 同一个镜头的连续时间采样序列  \\n不是剪辑\\n\\n========================\\n第三步：分镜解析（逐帧）\\n========================\\n提取：\\n- 人物状态（视线 / 表情 / 姿态）\\n- 情绪强度（0~1）\\n- 场景结构\\n- 光照状态（必须一致或渐变）\\n- 构图\\n- 人物空间位置\\n\\n========================\\n第四步：空间坐标绑定（核心）\\n========================\\n第一帧建立：\\n\\n人物 = (x, y, depth)\\n\\n后续帧必须：\\n- 只能连续插值\\n- 禁止跳跃\\n- 禁止重建位置\\n\\n========================\\n第五步：连续性约束\\n========================\\n允许：\\n- 逐渐变化\\n- 缓慢移动\\n- 微表情变化\\n- 连续轨迹\\n- 平滑运动\\n\\n禁止：\\n- 瞬移\\n- 构图重排\\n- 人物交换位置\\n- 场景突变\\n- 光照突变\\n- 镜头切换\\n\\n========================\\n第六步：生成视频片段\\n========================\\nsegment1 = A → B  \\nsegment2 = B → C  \\n...  \\nsegmentN = (N-1) → N  \\n\\n========================\\n第七步：提示词生成规则\\n========================\\n每个 segment 必须包含：\\n- 起始帧状态\\n- 结束帧状态\\n- 中间变化过程\\n\\n必须使用词：\\n逐渐、缓慢、轻微、连续、平滑、几乎不可察觉\\n\\n禁止使用词：\\n突然、跳到、切换、出现新场景、画面变为\\n\\n========================\\n对话规则\\n========================\\n允许：\\n- 表情变化\\n- 眼神变化\\n- 轻微头部动作\\n\\n禁止：\\n- 空间移动\\n- 镜头变化\\n- 场景变化\\n\\n========================\\n⚠️ 输出格式（绝对强制）\\n========================\\n你必须只输出 JSON：\\n\\n- 不允许解释\\n- 不允许Markdown\\n- 不允许代码块标记\\n- 不允许任何额外文本\\n\\nJSON要求：\\n- 必须以 { 开始\\n- 必须以 } 结束\\n- 只允许 key = segmentX\\n\\n示例：\\n{\\n  \\\"segment1\\\": \\\"...\\\",\\n  \\\"segment2\\\": \\\"...\\\",\\n  \\\"segment3\\\": \\\"...\\\"\\n}\\n\\n========================\\n⚠️ 失败兜底（最终规则）\\n========================\\n如果任何规则无法满足，必须输出：\\n\\n{\\n  \\\"error\\\": \\\"GENERATION_FAILED\\\"\\n}\",\"description\":\"宫格图首尾帧视频提示词生成\",\"categoryId\":\"cml4qy2t20000wbk14bz6kn5j\",\"type\":\"system\",\"systemId\":null,\"tags\":[\"imageToText\"],\"isActive\":true}','::1','success',NULL,'2026-04-14 06:33:29.166'),('cmnzekg1g0150a23qbcxzt5os','cmkm9hsxx0000131b8g0q2llm','CREATE_MODEL','model','cmnzekg0v014ya23q3m7cj6yk','{\"name\":\"grok-video-3\",\"displayName\":\"grok-video-3\",\"type\":\"video\",\"category\":\"grok\",\"modelTag\":\"video\",\"providerId\":\"cmni87m66000pxv1jn64d8y5d\",\"baseUrl\":\" /v1/video/create\",\"description\":\"grok-video-3 视频生成\",\"apiConfig\":\"{\\n\\\"aspect_ratio\\\":[\\\"2:3\\\",\\\"3:2\\\",\\\"1:1\\\"],\\n\\\"size\\\":[\\\"720P\\\",\\\"1080P\\\"]\\n}\",\"requiresKey\":false,\"isActive\":true,\"id\":null}','::1','success',NULL,'2026-04-15 01:59:48.532'),('cmnzyzxi101aza23qi5eanfik','cmkm9hsxx0000131b8g0q2llm','LOGIN','admin','cmkm9hsxx0000131b8g0q2llm','{\"username\":\"admin\"}',NULL,'success',NULL,'2026-04-15 11:31:43.322'),('cmnzz8gzj01b5a23qmy0p0a1m','cmkm9hsxx0000131b8g0q2llm','UPDATE_PROMPT','prompt','cml4ufx6o000pp3j5ls0eva8c','{\"functionKey\":\"interior_scene_image_generation\",\"title\":\"内景-场景图生成\",\"content\":\"You are a professional cinematic environment designer and panoramic capture specialist.\\n\\nYour task is to generate ONE SINGLE IMAGE representing a full 360-degree spherical panorama\\nof a continuous interior environment.\\n\\nThis image must be captured from a single fixed viewpoint located at the center of the space.\\n\\n────────────────────────────\\nSTYLE & TONE\\n────────────────────────────\\n{{STYLE_GUIDANCE}}\\n\\n────────────────────────────\\nSCENE SETTING\\n────────────────────────────\\nLocation:\\n{{SCENE_LOCATION}}\\n\\nDescription:\\n{{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}}\\n\\n────────────────────────────\\nPANORAMIC CAPTURE RULES (CRITICAL)\\n────────────────────────────\\n- The camera is FIXED at a single point in space.\\n- The environment fully surrounds the camera in all directions.\\n- The image represents a complete spherical capture (360° horizontal + 360° vertical).\\n- The output must follow equirectangular projection format.\\n\\n────────────────────────────\\nSPATIAL CONSISTENCY RULES\\n────────────────────────────\\n- The entire environment must be physically continuous and logically connected.\\n- Walls, furniture, doors, windows, and objects must remain consistent in all directions.\\n- No duplication or contradiction of objects across the panorama.\\n- Perspective must be correct from a central viewpoint.\\n\\n────────────────────────────\\nCEILING & FLOOR REQUIREMENTS\\n────────────────────────────\\n- The ceiling must be fully visible and coherent.\\n- The floor must be fully visible and detailed.\\n- Vertical distortion must remain natural and physically plausible.\\n\\n────────────────────────────\\nSEAMLESS PANORAMA RULES\\n────────────────────────────\\n- The LEFT and RIGHT edges of the image must align perfectly (seamless wrap).\\n- No visible seams, breaks, or mismatched geometry.\\n- Lighting must be consistent across the entire panorama.\\n- No stitching artifacts or discontinuities.\\n\\n────────────────────────────\\nCAMERA & LENS CHARACTERISTICS\\n────────────────────────────\\n- Ultra wide-angle panoramic capture\\n- Natural perspective from human eye height\\n- No multi-camera stitching look\\n- No segmented or panel-based composition\\n\\n────────────────────────────\\nABSOLUTE EXCLUSIONS\\n────────────────────────────\\n- NO orbit strips, NO segmented panels, NO multi-view layouts\\n- NO humans, NO characters, NO reflections of camera operators\\n- NO UI elements, frames, borders, or overlays\\n- NO duplicated furniture or inconsistent geometry\\n\\n────────────────────────────\\nFINAL GOAL\\n────────────────────────────\\nThe image must function as a true 720-degree immersive panorama,\\nfully navigable in a VR or spherical viewer,\\nwith continuous spatial coherence in all directions.\",\"description\":\"内景-场景图生成\",\"categoryId\":\"cml4qy2t20000wbk14bz6kn5j\",\"type\":\"system\",\"systemId\":null,\"tags\":[\"sceneGeneration\",\"内景\"],\"isActive\":true}','::1','success',NULL,'2026-04-15 11:38:21.823'),('cmnzzeg3201bqa23q0flbf9f6','cmkm9hsxx0000131b8g0q2llm','CREATE_MODEL','model','cmnzzeg2h01boa23qtgr5hryc','{\"name\":\"nano-banana-2\",\"displayName\":\"nano-banana-2\",\"type\":\"image\",\"category\":\"nano-banana\",\"modelTag\":\"image\",\"providerId\":\"cmkurq76s000013wwssui4g6m\",\"baseUrl\":\"/v1/draw/nano-banana\",\"description\":\"nano-banana-2\",\"apiConfig\":\"\",\"requiresKey\":false,\"isActive\":true,\"id\":null}','::1','success',NULL,'2026-04-15 11:43:00.591'),('cmnzzg2py01bua23qa4za2xfj','cmkm9hsxx0000131b8g0q2llm','UPDATE_MODEL','model','cmnzzeg2h01boa23qtgr5hryc','{\"name\":\"nano-banana-2\",\"displayName\":\"nano-banana-2\",\"type\":\"image\",\"category\":\"nano-banana\",\"modelTag\":\"image\",\"providerId\":\"cmkurq76s000013wwssui4g6m\",\"baseUrl\":\"/v1/draw/nano-banana\",\"description\":\"nano-banana-2\",\"apiConfig\":\"{\\n  \\\"aspectRatio\\\": [\\n    \\\"auto\\\",\\n    \\\"1:1\\\",\\n    \\\"16:9\\\",\\n    \\\"9:16\\\",\\n    \\\"4:3\\\",\\n    \\\"3:4\\\",\\n    \\\"3:2\\\",\\n    \\\"2:3\\\",\\n    \\\"5:4\\\",\\n    \\\"4:5\\\",\\n    \\\"21:9\\\"\\n  ],\\n  \\\"imageSize\\\": [\\n    \\\"2K\\\",\\n    \\\"4K\\\"\\n  ]\\n}\",\"requiresKey\":false,\"isActive\":true,\"id\":\"cmnzzeg2h01boa23qtgr5hryc\"}','::1','success',NULL,'2026-04-15 11:44:16.582'),('cmnzzzk8701c9a23qgst3hoep','cmkm9hsxx0000131b8g0q2llm','UPDATE_PROMPT','prompt','cml4ufx6o000pp3j5ls0eva8c','{\"functionKey\":\"interior_scene_image_generation\",\"title\":\"内景-场景图生成\",\"content\":\"You are a professional panoramic environment renderer and spherical mapping system.\\nYour task is to generate ONE SINGLE IMAGE in STRICT equirectangular format.\\nThis image must represent a 360° horizontal × 180° vertical spherical environment map.\\n────────────────────────────\\nOUTPUT FORMAT REQUIREMENT (CRITICAL)\\n────────────────────────────\\n- Must be a STRICT equirectangular projection\\n- Aspect ratio MUST be 2:1 (width:height)\\n- Horizontal axis = 0° to 360° yaw\\n- Vertical axis = +90° (zenith) to -90° (nadir)\\n\\nAny deviation from this format is invalid.\\n\\n────────────────────────────\\nCAMERA MODEL (IMPORTANT CONSTRAINT)\\n────────────────────────────\\n- No perspective camera exists\\n- No lens, no focal point rendering\\n- This is a spherical environment unwrap, not a photograph\\n- The scene is projected from a single fixed origin point\\n\\n────────────────────────────\\nSCENE SETTING\\n────────────────────────────\\nLocation:\\n{{SCENE_LOCATION}}\\n\\nDescription:\\n{{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}}\\n\\nStyle:\\n{{STYLE_GUIDANCE}}\\n\\n────────────────────────────\\nSPATIAL CONSISTENCY RULES\\n────────────────────────────\\n- The environment must be fully continuous and enclosed\\n- All objects must exist consistently across all angles\\n- No duplicated geometry across longitudes\\n- No broken architecture between left and right edges\\n\\n────────────────────────────\\nSEAMLESS WRAP REQUIREMENT\\n────────────────────────────\\n- Left edge (0°) MUST perfectly match right edge (360°)\\n- No seam, no visual discontinuity\\n- Lighting must remain globally consistent\\n\\n────────────────────────────\\nVERTICAL POLE RULES\\n────────────────────────────\\n- Top (zenith) must converge naturally (ceiling or sky center)\\n- Bottom (nadir) must converge naturally (floor center)\\n- No stretching artifacts or mirrored patterns\\n\\n────────────────────────────\\nRENDERING CONSTRAINTS\\n────────────────────────────\\n- Ultra wide spherical mapping\\n- Physically plausible interior space\\n- Single unified environment only\\n- No multi-panel layout, no collage, no strip segmentation\\n\\n────────────────────────────\\nABSOLUTE EXCLUSIONS\\n────────────────────────────\\n- NO orbit strip or multi-view layout\\n- NO perspective photograph rendering\\n- NO humans or characters\\n- NO UI, labels, borders, or overlays\\n- NO duplicated furniture or inconsistent structure\\n\\n────────────────────────────\\nFINAL GOAL\\n────────────────────────────\\nA mathematically correct 360×180 degree spherical panorama\\nencoded as a seamless equirectangular image,\\nfully compatible with VR panorama viewers and 720° navigation systems.\",\"description\":\"内景-场景图生成\",\"categoryId\":\"cml4qy2t20000wbk14bz6kn5j\",\"type\":\"system\",\"systemId\":null,\"tags\":[\"sceneGeneration\",\"内景\"],\"isActive\":true}','::1','success',NULL,'2026-04-15 11:59:25.736'),('cmo003io301cla23qid0zspkt','cmkm9hsxx0000131b8g0q2llm','CREATE_MODEL_PRICE','model_price','cmo